				<td colspan="2"><span>Yesterday I tried pulling Vindi for the first time.  Usually there are two monks there to lull the two adds then pull vindi solo but that was not an option this time.  Only one monk and he tried to fd split but ended up with the three of them stacked on the bridge.  I tell him to let me try so I pull them out past the wall then use deftdance and highsun to send back the two and then fade to loose agro.
<br />

<br />
At this point Vindi is standing alone and I am outside agro range so the monk tells the MT to tag.  I start heading back to the raid when i notice that the two adds are heading back to help vindi.  Do these adds agro if vindi is or did I or the monk not lose agro?  I am sure the monk thinks it was me who kept agro and I think it was him but just checking to make sure my method is sound before we try again.</span></td>
