				<td colspan="2"><span>I have never been able to get Vindi single and leave the two Temple Guardians up and back in the temple -- they are agro-tied to him.  If you agro him, you agro them whether or not they have been lulled.  We killed Vindi the other night for his heart.  We had two groups and it was very very easy.  Warrior tanked Vindi, a Paladin off-tanked one of the temple guardians and I kept highsunning the other one.  Took us about 90 seconds to take out Vindi and no time at all to kill the guardians after.
<br />

<br />
Back in the day, the guardians walked down to the bridge with Vindi.  It was possible to pull all three out into the middle of the arena and highsun Vindi back to his spawn.  He would still be agrod, but he would get stuck pathing into the ice wall and not add until after you killed the guardians.  They don't path the same way any more.</span></td>
