<br />

<br />
I then waited at the bottom of the steps and Highsunned the Temple Guardians back whilst the raid killed Vindi. Only problem I see here is if the Temple Guardians agro any repops on the way through, but this shouldn't be a problem providing you clear and pull Vindi straight away.
