				<td colspan="2"><span>The Ultimate Secret to Single Vindi Pulls!
<br />

<br />
Pull Vindi when he is nearest the temple, this way you can watch his 2 temple gaurds run with him.  Drag them out to a nice empty arena and start running in circles, slowly run a tighter circle until in casting range of vindi.  then high sun him, fade and aggro the 2 temple gaurdians who are going to start running back to vindi immedietely.  Drag them to raid, kill and then pull vindi single.  Works every single time.  Vindi is not chained to gaurds, gaurds are chained to him.  You fade only to clear vindi aggro who will warp to the raid otherwise.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
